{
  "_name": "04 — Denoise then Upscale (NVIDIA RTX pipeline)",
  "_description": [
    "MODEL REQUIRED:",
    "  NVIDIA RTX VSR model files — download the NVIDIA Video Effects SDK:",
    "  https://developer.nvidia.com/rtx-video-sdk",
    "  Verify: python scripts/check_environment.py",
    "",
    "Two-stage NVIDIA RTX enhancement pipeline:",
    "  Stage 1 → RTX Denoise       (removes compression noise and grain)",
    "  Stage 2 → RTX VSR 4x        (upscales the clean frame)",
    "",
    "This is the recommended order: always denoise BEFORE upscaling.",
    "Upscaling noise first makes artifacts larger and harder to remove.",
    "",
    "Required nodes:",
    "  - RTXVSRSingleFrameNode   (our custom node, comfyui/custom_nodes/)",
    "  - RTXDenoiseNode          (from Comfy-Org/Nvidia_RTX_Nodes_ComfyUI)",
    "    OR use 'NNLatentUpscale' / any denoising node as a substitute",
    "    if the official NVIDIA denoise node is not available.",
    "",
    "NOTE: If RTXDenoiseNode is not installed, bypass node 2 by connecting",
    "  LoadImage directly to RTXVSRSingleFrameNode (link 1 → node 3).",
    "",
    "Node chain:",
    "  LoadImage ──► RTX Denoise ──► RTX VSR 4x ──► SaveImage"
  ],
